title: 10,000 Hours
itunes:title: 10,000 Hours
description:
Episode 377 - Have you heard of the 10,000 hour rule? It is one of my favorite concepts. Why? Because to me it means that we can do anything that we want to if we are willing to dedicate our lives to it. Tune in to today's episode as I speak about this empowering concept!
